(48, '2020-07-31 12:12:19', 18, 2, '<div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>W41/41, Freitag der 24. Juli 2020</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Fris<u>eu</u>r</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Friseurin</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">(note: e Friseuse / e Fris&ouml;se &hellip;.. a little obsolete)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Sal<u>o</u>n, s, s</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">der Salon meines Friseurs</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">der Salon meine<strong>r </strong>Friseurin</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">von + D</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">in der N&auml;he von dir</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Pause, -, n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">verbringen, h. verbracht</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans