\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Jeden Tag hatten wir zwei Vorlesungen.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Besprechung, en<br />session, meeting</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">s Seminar, s, e<br />seminar</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Es hat in der Gruppe 20 Studenten gegeben.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><u><span style=\"background: yellow;\">an</span></u> etwas (D) <u><span style=\"background: lime;\">teil</span></u><span style=\"background: lime;\">/nehmen</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background: yellow;\">in</span> st <span style=\"background: lime;\">participate</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Letzte Woche habe ich viele Hausaufgaben gemacht.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Augabe, n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">I participate in the course.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich nehme an dem Kurs (am Kurs) teil.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">I participated in the course.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich habe an dem Kurs teilgenommen.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Nur 8 bis 10 Stundenten haben an dem Seminar</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">aktiv teilgenommen.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">sogar&hellip;. even</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">an der Universit&auml;t</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Sogar an der Universit&auml;t sind 50 % der Stundenten</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">nicht aktiv.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Der Kurs war sehr intensiv.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">einen Film schauen</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">to watch a movie</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ich habe Filme geschaut</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich hatte <strong>&uuml;berhaupt </strong>keine Freizeit.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich hatte <strong>gar </strong>keine Freizeit.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">es ist gro&szlig;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">es ist nicht gro&szlig; &hellip;. it&rsquo;s not big</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background: aqua;\">es ist <strong>&uuml;berhaupt </strong>nicht gro&szlig; </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background: aqua;\">es ist <strong>gar </strong>nicht gro&szlig;</span> &hellip;.. it&rsquo;s not big at all</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Untertitel, -</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">subtitle</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">mit Untertitel<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">n</span> &hellip; dative plural -n ending</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Film, e</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Name, n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">der Name de<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">s </span></strong>Film<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">es </span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich kenne dich / ihn</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich kenne <strong>den</strong> Namen des Filmes nicht.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich kenne nicht den Names des Filmes.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich kann dir den Link schicken.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Lass dir Zeit. <br />Take your time.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Wenige Filme gefallen mir.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Geschichte</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">1/ story</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">2/ history</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Schauspieler</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">schwach x stark</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">weak x strong</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">po<u>e</u>tisch</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Film</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Regisseur, e</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">film director</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Man hat den / diesen Film 1929 gemacht.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Welle,&nbsp; n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">wave</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">in den sechziger Jahren</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">in den Sechzigern &ndash; V &ndash; S</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><u>In den Sechzigern</u> hat man in Frankreich, in D. und in</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">vielen anderen L&auml;ndern viele sehr gute Filme gemacht.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">in den Zwanzigern und Drei&szlig;igern hat man in vielen</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">L&auml;ndern viele sehr gute Filme gemacht.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Vorreiter, s, -</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">front runner</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">verlassen (er vel&auml;sst, h. verlassen)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">to leave, to abandon</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Krieg, e<br />war</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">wahrscheinlich</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">probably, probable</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">entdecken</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">to discover</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">entwickeln</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">to develop</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">erfinden</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">to invent</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich habe <strong>&uuml;berhaupt / gar </strong>keine Hausaufgaben</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">gemacht.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich hatte <strong>&uuml;berhaupt </strong>keine Zeit.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich hatte <strong>gar </strong>keine Zeit.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">vor/schlagen</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ich schlage vor</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">du schl&auml;gst vor&hellip;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">to suggest</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Wendung, en</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">phrase, expression</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; fon