(49, '2020-07-31 12:20:19', 18, 2, '<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>Freitag der 31. Juni, W 42/42</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Konversation</h1>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">stolz auf etwas (A)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">proud of st</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Sorge, n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">worry, concern</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ernst</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">serious</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">traurig</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">sad</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Geduld, 0</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">patience</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Wie sp&auml;t ist es jetzt?</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">dunkel x hell</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">dark x light</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">auf/machen x zu/machen</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">to open x to close</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich habe meine Fenster aufgemacht.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Vorhang, &auml;-e<br />curtain</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich glaube, dass das Wetter morgen k&auml;lter ist.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">kalt &ndash; k&auml;lter</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">(sich) entscheiden</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ei &gt;&gt; ie</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">h. entschieden</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich habe <strong>mich </strong>entschieden, dass <strong>ich </strong>heute mit meinem Bruder zu einer Ausstellung <strong>gehe.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Ausstellung, en</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">exhibition</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Kunst gef&auml;llt ihm / meiner Schwester / ihr.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">in den N&auml;he von &hellip; close to</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">in Barbican</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">das Thema der Ausstellung</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich hoffe, dass diese A. sehr interessant ist.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Wessen Idee war <strong>es</strong>?</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Es war meine Idee.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Es war die/eine Idee <u>meines Bruders.</u></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Es war <u>seine</u> Idee.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Mein Bruder geht manchmal in Ausstellungen.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Wir haben <strong>uns </strong>entschieden, dass wir zusammen essen wollen.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">x</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Die Regierung hat entschieden &hellip;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Regenschirm, e</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Sonnenschirm, e</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich glaube, dass <strong>ein </strong>Regenschirm akzeptabler ist.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">akzeptabel &ndash; akzeptabler</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">flexibel &ndash; flexibler</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">In England muss man sehr flexibel sein.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich bin auch nicht posh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Brille, n (sg)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">glasses</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Normalerweise &ndash; V &ndash; S &ndash;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Normalerweise tragen die Leute in England H&uuml;te.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich meine, dass Leute im Sommer H&uuml;te tragen.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Das stimmt.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">that&rsquo;s right, that&rsquo;s correct</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">einer Sache / jemandem (D) zu/stimmen</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ich stimme dir zu<br />I agree with you</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ich stimme dem Plan zu</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">I agree with the plan</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">stimmen</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">to agree (to have the right tuning)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Stimme, n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">voice</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Wendung, en</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">phrase, expression</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">---------- <br />nach</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">1/ &hellip; ich fahre nach Berlin, Frankreich</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">(ich gehe nach Hause&hellip;. exception)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">2/ after</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">s Land</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">auf dem Lande / auf dem Land</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">s Jahr</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">im Jahre &hellip; im Jahr</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">---------</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Prepositions in German so far</h1>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-top: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">with the D</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>with the A &hellip; <u>f&uuml;r, ohne, gegen</u>, durch, um </strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">with A/D &nbsp;<br />wohin?... A <br />wo? &hellip;&hellip;. D</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich habe ein Geschenk f&uuml;r dich. <br />Ich habe nichts gegen ihn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich reise ohne meinen Koffer.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Wir gehen durch den Park.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Wir gehen um den Park.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">nicht x nicht<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">s </span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">negating particle x nothing</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich setze mich an den Tisch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich sitze am Tisch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">N</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">A</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">D</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">G</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Wortstellung</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">word order</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><strong>&sect;44 in L7</strong></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">bitten &ndash; ich habe gebeten</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">I asked my brother for a table.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich habe meinen Bruder <strong>um</strong> einen Tisch gebeten.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">bitten jemanden um etwas</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">r Kellner, -</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Ich habe den Kellner um ein Glas Wasser gebeten.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">e Minute, n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&hellip;. <u>wir <strong>sind</strong></u>&hellip;&hellip; <u>abgebogen</u></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">er<strong> ist</strong> abgebogen</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">er hat gesessen</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ich habe gesetzt</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">x</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">ich bin aufgestanden</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">legen</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">liegen</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">------</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Wir k&ouml;nnen uns am Mittwoch um 15 treffen.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>Passt es Ihnen / dir / euch?</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Does it suit you?</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Der Kuli ist vom Tisch gefallen.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Es gef&auml;llt mir .</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Es hat mir gefallen.</p>', '<div>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-top: 0px;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-align: left;\">Skype trail + vocab</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-align: left;\">look through the corrected work</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-align: left;\">finish off L7/6, 8 &hellip;. check with the solution booklet</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-align: left;\">&sect;44 + exercise on the bottom <br />L&amp;T 6-9<br />L7/ 10, 9, 11, <strong>12, 13</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>', '<div>konv. ... cest. do Nemecka, vystava&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>dotazy v mejlu k L&amp;T</div>\r\n<div>predlozky - D&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>N - Wendungen L7 + 7</div>\r\n<div>refl. slovesa&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', '<div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong><span lang=\"DE\">Freitag der 31. Juni, W 42/42</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">konv.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-s