span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">britisch &nbsp;(adj.)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Der Arzt war Brite. &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Die OP endet um halb neun abends.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Die OP hat um &hellip;&hellip;.. geendet.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Und Emily hat <strong>mich</strong> um 10 Uhr abgeholt.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong><span lang=\"DE\">Wen</span></strong><span lang=\"DE\"> hat Emily abgeholt?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">nach der OP, vor der OP</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">nach D</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Man darf von einer Operation nichts essen.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Hat dir das Essen im K. geschmeckt?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Ich hatte einen gro&szlig;en Hunger, deshalb &ndash; V &ndash; S &hellip;.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 108pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-indent: 36pt;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&hellip;. deshalb hat mir das Essen geschmeckt.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">ich war der letzte Patient</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">e Pflege, 0</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">care</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Nach dieser Deutschstunde <s>gehe</s> <strong>fahre </strong>ich nach Marylebone und &hellip;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">seit einer Woche habe ich Halsschmerzen</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Der Arzt hat mich am Dienstagnachmittag angerufen.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Er hat <s>mir</s> <strong>mich</strong> gefragt: Wie f&uuml;hlst du dich? / Wie f&uuml;hlen Sie sich?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">ich frage dich</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">fragen A</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">x</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">antworten D</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">ich antworte dir</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">sprechen x sagen</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">to speak x to say, to tell</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">ich sage dir</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Der Arzt hat mir gesagt, <span style=\"background: lime;\">dass die OP gut gegange</span>n ist.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Die OP <strong>ist </strong>gut gegangen.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Wie <strong>seid </strong>ihr nach Hause <strong>gereist</strong>?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Wir <strong>sind </strong>mit Uber nach Hause <strong>gereist.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Ich hatte noch Hunger.<br />I was still hungry.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Ich konnte nach der OP nicht schlafen.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Du hast Hunger, du isst viel, aber du wirst nicht dick.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">s Gen, e</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">schlank x dick</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">slim x fat</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">stark x schwach</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">strong x weak</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">besonders</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">especially</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Mein Chef hat <strong>mir </strong>einen Nachricht geschickt.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Er hat mich gefragt: &bdquo;Wie f&uuml;hlst du dich?&ldquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Er hat mich gefragt, <span style=\"background: lime;\">wie S ------------------- V</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;NEBENSATZ</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">He asked me how I felt.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Er hat mich gefragt, wie ich mich f&uuml;hle.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Ich habe ihm geantwortet: &bdquo;Ich f&uuml;hle mich gut.&ldquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Ich habe ihm geantwortet, dass ich mich gut f&uuml;hle.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">antworten &ndash; geantwortet</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">spielen &ndash; gespielt</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">kochen &ndash; gekocht</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">arbeiten &ndash; gearbeitet</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Wir haben am Samstag gesprochen.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Ich habe sie angerufen.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">Sie sind zufrieden, dass die OP gut gegangen ist.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">e Sorge, n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">worry, concern</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"DE\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size